Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:09.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:20.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:38.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:46.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:59.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:06.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:14.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:20.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.04,0:01:28.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:32.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,You say it's a Simoun from Arcus Niger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Military Councilor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Military Councilor!\NWhat's the meaning of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Arcus Niger...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:48.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:51.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o'clock! Five ancient\NSimouns approaching fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:07.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sortie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Four o'clock! Multiple aircraft sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry, confirm that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,They appear to be\NShoukoku cruise missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura, take one of the similes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:18.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:20.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which way should we head?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:23.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's right. They say the\Nenemy Simouns are here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:26.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to destroy the\Nmissiles headed toward the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:28.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,What about the Highland Simouns?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Arcus Prima and the Messis...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:32.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will have to meet the\Nattack without our protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:38.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have to give it our best shot.\NThat's all we can do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock! More aircraft approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me what they are and how many!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:12.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shoukoku cruise missiles!\NTwenty of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:18.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon! Three o'clock,\Nmore missiles headed our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:28.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether it's a Ri Majon to\Nhonor the souls of the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or a Ri Majon to repulse the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a Ri Majon is still a Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's what I used to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:10.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:20.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, the shrapnel\Nis falling over the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's just too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:39.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now I know that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're both Ri Majons, but they're\Nfor a completely different purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:46.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:04:59.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you two all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas is hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:11.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's nothing. What about\Nyou, Roatreamon? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:14.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, what about the enemy Simouns?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:20.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,The thing is... I can't be sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,They seem to have flown off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:23.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're turning around and flying away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you absolutely sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:31.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Plumbum enemy Simouns\Nare about to leave our sights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the enemy Simouns attack us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know. But if they had attacked us,\Nthey might have gotten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:52.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your quarters, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:55.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:07.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Military Councilor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:24.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,The simile transporting Sibylla\NMamina's body never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:29.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm certain it was\Nintercepted by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:33.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Needless to say, this happened\Nwithin the Kyuukoku borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meaning we've already lost\Ncontrol of our own airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what about Sibylla Mamina's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:46.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, that hardly matters anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't you see we're in a state of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't you see we're in a state of...\NSo it's no concern of ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what happens to Sibylla Mamina's\Nbody. Is that what you're saying, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:57.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are not to inform the\Nsibyllae of this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this! Even you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:05.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,The fact that the enemy Simouns\Nshowed up in battle today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:10.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was a taunt to let us know\Nthey can attack us at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:14.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that's exactly\Nwhat they're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:34.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't believe such a thing\Ncould've happened while we were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,There must be something\Nwe can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,How are you holding up, Sibylla Morinas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:56.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:08:00.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Waporif, are you good\Nat wrapping bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had no idea Roatreamon\Nwas so bad at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:10.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, allow me, Sibylla Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,You see, the doctor was busy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:16.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,He's gone to the great temple,\Ntending to the injured civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm leaving her\Nin your hands then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:21.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:25.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:30.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,We still have a lot of\Nthings to do, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:37.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, I like the Ri Majons\Nthat we offer to Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:42.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you know what? I bet\Neveryone else feels the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:43.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,How bad is the damage to the Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:01.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll only\Nhave to replace the canopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:05.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,We just finished repairing Sibylla\NAurea's Simoun, and now this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:09.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was there no other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:12.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, there really wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to take\Nbetter care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:51.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no longer any way to engage\Nthe Shoukoku-highlands alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...who took away three of the Simoun\Nsibyllae at such a critical time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's be clear about\Nwho's responsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:05.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe the situation is well\Npast the point of assigning blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,We really should return to\Nthe purpose of this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:14.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,One hour ago, the\NShoukoku-highlands alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:18.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...offered Simulacrum\NKyuukoku a cease-fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:21.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that they have a\Nclear advantage over us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they're actually suing for peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've\Nalready forgotten how...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the highlands negotiated\Npeace the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:32.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it is our people's desire to bring\Nan end to this war as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:35.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can't you see that their\Noffer is nothing but a sham?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not again...\NThis wouldn't have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:37.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not again...\N...if you'd tried to negotiate peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:38.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,...if you'd tried to negotiate peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of your petty grudges!\N...if you'd tried to negotiate peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not fit for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not true, Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:56.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what you may think\Nyourself, you are a Simoun sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:00.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,All I know is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:04.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was a warrior too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:13.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so, her prayers brought\Nsolace to many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:17.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone flocked to\NAmuria to be blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,The priestesses are going\Nto protect us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:26.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The priestesses are going to\Nstrike down all the bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:29.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right. Just be\Npatient a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:31.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. I didn't\Nthink you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:12:00.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril and Aer are\Nblessing the people outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who ever thought we'd\Nsee Aer doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:09.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're the one we'd expect to\Ntake the initiative... Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think she should be by your side, Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't really explain why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but I want you to\Nhold on to this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:57.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, will you look after\NMamina for me from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:15.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd\Nhide anything from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it that you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just don't know anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do I want from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:40.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Emergency! Guys, it's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:47.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! We just heard that they're\Nasking for another peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, Floe just told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:55.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,But is that information true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sibylla Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did the information come from you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only a handful of\Npeople are aware of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I took it upon myself to inform you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:10.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,So is the war really\Ngoing to end this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Remember, Anglas was\Nsupposed to be visiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Kyuukoku as an interpreter\Nfor the peace conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know, but maybe this time around...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:30.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's possible that this time we'll be\Nable to release you sibyllae from battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, there's\Nnothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can only do what we\Nhave the power to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, I'd like to\Ndiscuss something with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea!\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta said the same thing just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,First off, to protect\Nourselves from being invaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...from the mountains,\Nlet us go out on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand it's a\Nstate of emergency, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just look at the size\Nof the Arcus Prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:18.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to believe that Arcus\NNiger, a ship of the same dimensions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...was actually shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:30.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just as hard to believe as\Nseeing you at odds with Guragief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:33.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine the\Ndepth of your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,...for each other that\Nneither of you can concede.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...too single-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:46.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a shame that he\Ndecided to become a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:55.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Try to make peace with\NGuragief as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,You might not have a lot\Nof time left with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:15:59.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to get back to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Kaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why are they attacking us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're going to keep at it\Nuntil they bend us to their will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:23.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cast off the moorings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Drop anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ascend at top speed! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ascending at top speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:47.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o'clock! Five ancient\NSimouns approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:52.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eleven o'clock, Shoukoku\Nmidrange aircraft approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Prepare the Simouns for takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:56.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where are the priestesses\Nfrom Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're not here yet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:06.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for, Anubituf?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Order Chor Tempest to go into battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:13.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain?\NPay no attention to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Communications officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:26.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Send word for the sibyllae to\Nstand by on the flight deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to convey my orders in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:29.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:32.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, I'm leaving\Nyou in charge for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Arcus Prima will launch\Nthe second wave of our attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:37.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'll be directing\Nthe Arcus Prima then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:39.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll be in command until\Nthe captain returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:44.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:48.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NGet up there already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our orders are to stand\Nby on the flight deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,What the!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Damn that Anubituf! What's he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:57.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Standing by at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Standing by at a time like this!\NThat old guy is so obnoxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:15.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,It may be hard to believe, but I too\Nwas once a sibylla just like all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're going to fly a Simile, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:23.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. We're going to have to meet the\Nenemy attack with only five Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:28.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going up in a Simile and will\Ngive you direct orders in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please follow those orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:31.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,How is your wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was given impeccable\Ntreatment, sir. Everything is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:45.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get that Simile ready to go. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:45.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,The time has come for\Nus to take you out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,...of this war that you've\Nbeen fighting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:17.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,But only because we have failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:20.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,We thank you, Captain Anubituf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:23.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, we\Nshall never forget your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:27.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no need to worry!\NWe've already made up our minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're just going to\Ngive it our best shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we have the power to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're hopelessly outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to draw them\Nin as close as we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:43.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...then make a sudden\Ndive and strike them hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:49.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,This first attack will\Ndecide the course of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:57.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:28.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,All batteries, fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,That'll show you, losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:06.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:09.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,How do you like that, jerks?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:14.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Both of you, watch your language!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You heard us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:21.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, but we were just saying that\Nyou two were probably talking vulgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:24.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:33.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll bet it's just Floe making\Nanother one of her absurd comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:36.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's probably\Nit, huh, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:37.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's insulting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never said anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never said anything like that!\NIs Chor Tempest always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:43.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Captain's Simile, approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:57.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everybody, hats off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:20.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Despite Chor Tempest's efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:25.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the center determined that\Nthe war was now a lost cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:28.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,And several days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:33.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,...accepted the peace treaty offered\Nby the Plumbum highlands and Shoukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:47.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:52.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:59.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:06.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:19.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:24.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:28.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:32.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:38.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:44.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.35,0:23:47.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:53.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:59.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:06.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:10.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,As alliance soldiers take\Ncontrol of the Arcus Prima...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.81,0:24:13.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Chor Tempest is disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.25,0:24:15.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:16.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eternal Maidens
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:17.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eternal Maidens\NEternal Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.95,0:24:19.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eternal Maidens
